Coming Soon Features
==========================
Description:
"Coming Soon" is intended to provide a Drupal implementation 
of LaunchRock, which is a signup and like/share website for
sites and projects that are currently in development. 
It is intended to provide a way to collect potential users
as you build the importance of your product, service or site 
before the actual launch.

==========================
Features:
-Signup to a mailing list via (project/mailing_list)
-Share with others via TweetButton, FB Like, and/or Google+1

==========================
